Description: This package is accompanying our final project for the Programming Tools class.  It encompasses a collection of functions integral to our Shiny application, which is designed to offer users a comprehensive view of their monthly budget. The package aims to facilitate an interactive and user-friendly experience, enabling users to effectively manage and visualize their financial data.
